          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>FAITHFULL has been proudly B-Corp Certified since 2021 and was recertified at the end of 2024.</p><p>B-Corp Certification is a whole business assessment of a company’s social and environmental performance. It is based on five key impact areas of Governance, Workers, Community, Environment and Customers.</p><p>The movement has connected a global network of high performing and mission-driven businesses that are committed to forces of good. This includes over 8000 certified businesses in 90 countries, 160 industries represented and 150,000 businesses applying the B Impact Assessment.</p><p>Following FAITHFULL’s recertification at the end of 2024, we reached a new high score of 118.4, improving our original score of 96.3. </p>",
