        "title_style": "h1",
        "title_alignment": "center",
        "title_alignment_mobile": "center",
        "text": "Becoming certified as a B Corporation goes beyond product or service level certification. B Corp is the only accreditation that measures a company’s entire social and environmental performance. The B Impact Assessment evaluates how a company’s operations and business model impact its workers, community, environment, and customers. From supply chain and input materials, to charitable giving and employee benefits, B Corp demonstrates a business meets - and maintains - a substantiated level of social and environmental responsibility across their entire operation.",
