        "text_YEQBQD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Governance",
            "description": "<p>FAITHFULL is an independent company with operations in both Bali, Indonesia and Sydney, Australia. We have revised our corporate governing documents for the inclusion of a stakeholder consideration clause, which we have integrated into formal decision-making processes. We have also established an internal Steering Committee to monitor environmental and social performance.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_teCEkg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Workers",
            "description": "<p>The highest scoring for FAITHFULL, we sit above-average and received a Best In World Award from B-Lab in 2022. Employees are valued at FAITHFULL with verified living wages, above-industry benefits, training opportunities and additional support programs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_L99mEx": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Community",
            "description": "<p>Both female-owned and led, with over 75% of managerial roles provided to women, we prioritise local manufacturing partners when able and maintain a positive corporate citizenship program with donations to a number of organisations across Indonesia, Australia and the world. Learn more about our values and commitments <a href=\"/pages/about\" title=\"About Us\">here</a>. </p>"
          }
        },
        "text_6EJN4J": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Environment",
            "description": "<p>While the fashion industry is known for its resource intensive practices, we consciously choose to produce products through the use of environmentally-preferred methods and materials, opting for certified fabrications and production processes including digital printing. We refuse to follow common industry practices like the burning of offcuts. Instead, we are always investigating new end-of-life strategies to account for the full lifecycle of each product. Learn more about our products and fabrications <a href=\"/pages/our-products\" title=\"Our Products\">here.</a></p>"
          }
        },
        "text_a3D9fV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Customers",
            "description": "<p>We have always and will continue to maintain a positive relationship with our community, offering above-average product warranty and quality assurance. Learn more about our customer protections <a href=\"/pages/our-products\" title=\"Our Products\">here. </a></p>"
          }
        }
